name: Apache DBCP - Database Connection Pooling Library
Consul client
patterns: ('Consul (maven)' or ('Discovery client (import)' and 'Consul (properties)')) and not 'Desactivated Consul (properties)'

name: AWS Lambda
patterns: ('AWS.Lambda(Java)' or 'Lambda Service Receive(javascript)') or ('Lambda Handler(javascript)' or ('AWS Lambda(YAML)' or ('Chalice' or 'AWS SDK Lambda(C#)')))

name: AWS Event Source S3
patterns: (('AWS S3 Event' or 'AWS S3 Event(Python)') or ('AWS.S3(Java)' or ('AWS S3 Event(C#)'or 'AWS S3 Event(Java)')))

name: AWS Event Source SNS
patterns: (('AWS SNS Event' or 'AWS SNS Event(Python)') or ('AWS SNS(Java)' or ('AWS SNS Event(C#)' or 'AWS SNS Event(Java)')))

name: AWS Event Source DynamoDB
patterns: (('AWS DynamoDB Event' or 'AWS DynamoDB Event(Python)') or ('AWS DynamoDB(Java)' or ('AWS DynamoDB Event(C#)' or 'AWS DynamoDB Event(Java)')))

name: AWS Event Source SQS
patterns: (('AWS SQS Event' or 'AWS SQS Event(Python)') or ('AWS SQS(Java)' or ('AWS SQS Event(C#)' or 'AWS SQS Event(Java)')))

name: AWS Event Source API
patterns: ('AWS API Event' or ('AWS API Event(Python)' or ('AWS API Event(C#)' or 'AWS API Event(Java)')))

name: AWS API Gateway
patterns: ('AWS API Event' or ('AWS API Event(Python)' or ('AWS API Event(C#)' or 'AWS API Event(Java)')))

name: AWS Event Source Cognito
patterns: ('AWS Cognito Event' or ('AWS Cognito (Java)' or ('AWS Cognito Event(C#)' or 'AWS Cognito Event(Java)')))

name: AWS CDK
patterns: ('AWS CDK (Java)' or 'AWS CDK (TypeScript)') or ('AWS CDK (C#)' or 'AWS CDK (Python)')

name: Technical(pattern)
patterns: (('Discovery service' or 'Monitoring service') or ('Turbine service' or 'Configuration service')) or (('Admin service' or 'API Gateway service') or 'Zipkin Tracing service')
